a few moments about when

00:02:32.830 --> 00:02:34.720
was the last time you
really felt, yes, I'm

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:38.320
really on top of this, this is
a moment of key productivity.

00:02:38.320 --> 00:02:40.397
Often, when people think
about that question,

00:02:40.397 --> 00:02:41.980
one of the answers
that comes up a lot

00:02:41.980 --> 00:02:43.420
is when I was on a deadline.

00:02:43.420 --> 00:02:44.774
So you're on this deadline.

00:02:44.774 --> 00:02:45.940
You've got this thing to do.

00:02:45.940 --> 00:02:47.749
It's got to be in
at five o'clock.

00:02:47.749 --> 00:02:48.790
You've got this deadline.

00:02:48.790 --> 00:02:50.800
And everything else in
your life and everything

00:02:50.800 --> 00:02:52.383
else in your brain
seems to fall away.

00:02:52.383 --> 00:02:54.130
And you get into
what psychologists

00:02:54.130 --> 00:02:56.050
refer to as flow,
this kind of state

00:02:56.050 --> 00:02:59.099
